            </div>
            <div class="info-card">
              <h4>Insurance Gaps</h4>
              <p>Standard renter's insurance does not cover short-term rental activity. Airbnb's AirCover has coverage limits and exclusions. Without a dedicated STR policy, you bear full personal liability for guest injuries, theft, and property damage to your landlord's unit.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

