            </div>
            <div class="info-card">
              <h4>Thin Margins</h4>
              <p>GTA rents are among the highest in Canada. One bad month, a slow season, or a single major guest incident can eliminate months of profit. The business has no meaningful buffer against volatility.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="info-card">
              <h4>Platform Risk</h4>
              <p>Airbnb can suspend listings for policy violations. If your listing is flagged as non-compliant with local regulations or if a guest complaint triggers a review, your revenue can disappear overnight. You have no recourse as a non-owner operator.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

